author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Shower valve tile tips…I’m using a 4-1/2 inch Drilax diamond hole saw with a Makita drill. The provided template works great with water to create smooth cuts. I’ve used this for homes in the center of large tiles as well. Many thanks to Makita for sending their 1/2” 18V LXT driver-drill 🔥
title: Shower Valve Tile Tips - #shorts #tileshower #homerepairtutor
